' ===== Strategy Interface =====
interface TransportOption {
    +getRoute(from: String, to: String): String
    +getPrice(): double
    +book(): void
}

note right of TransportOption
  Strategy interface:
  definieert gedrag van verschillende
  vervoersopties (zoals auto, trein, etc.)
end note

